{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>&quot;The Hallways&quot;</strong> is a short horror game where you explore a maze of dark corridors. As you walk through the hallways, you\u2019ll sense that something unsettling is always nearby. Can you figure out the mystery behind the place, or will you get lost in its endless twists and turns?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2823310/extras/PageHeader.png?t=1727977190\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2823310/extras/Atmosphere.gif?t=1727977190\" /><strong>You play as Emma, who wakes up in a weird place with no idea how she got there.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>With only a flashlight, you're tasked with making sense of the series of confusing hallways that change every time you think you've got the layout down.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2823310/extras/PageFlashlight.png?t=1727977190\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2823310/extras/SpectralLight.gif?t=1727977190\" /><strong>The flashlight isn't just for the dark, it also shows you clues and paths you</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>can't see with your own eyes. The place is full of secrets and it's up to you to piece them</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>together to find a way out.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2823310/extras/PageHighlights.png?t=1727977190\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2823310/extras/Inspection.gif?t=1727977190\" /> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Always Changing:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> The hallways shift and change, making each walk through them a new challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A Special Light:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Use your flashlight to reveal hidden messages and escape routes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Spooky Vibes:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> If you're into games that give you the creeps, you're in the right place.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>No Fighting, Just Frightening:</strong> It's not about fighting monsters, it's about surviving the fear.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2823310/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1727977190","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2823310/page.bg.jpg?t=1727977190","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2823310/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1727977190","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2823310/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1727977190","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"The Hallways contains intense violence, blood and gore, as well as horror themes and occasional nudity."},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>&quot;The Hallways&quot;</strong> is a short horror game where you explore a maze of dark corridors. As you walk through the hallways, you\u2019ll sense that something unsettling is always nearby. Can you figure out the mystery behind the place, or will you get lost in its endless twists and turns?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2823310/extras/PageHeader.png?t=1727977190\" /><